WEBVTT

STYLE
::cue {
font-size: 1em;
font-weight: bold;
color: #ffffff;
}

00:01:31.180 --> 00:01:34.700 line:80%
=Generation to Generation=

00:01:34.820 --> 00:01:37.740 line:80%
=Episode 8=

00:01:38.370 --> 00:01:40.290 line:80%
Duan Jiuxiu, Elder Tianji

00:01:41.010 --> 00:01:42.650 line:80%
was already killed by my aunt.

00:01:43.780 --> 00:01:44.620 line:80%
Uncle Zhou,

00:01:45.980 --> 00:01:47.650 line:80%
why is he still alive?

00:01:49.730 --> 00:01:50.570 line:80%
Zhizhen,

00:01:51.570 --> 00:01:52.410 line:80%
are you all right?

00:01:52.421 --> 00:01:54.262 line:80%
(Young Zhou Zhizhen, Peiqiong Manor)
I'm fine.

00:01:54.273 --> 00:01:55.010 line:80%
Pingshu is injured.

00:01:55.060 --> 00:01:56.694 line:80%
(Young Zhou Zhiqin)
I'll escort her back.

00:01:58.210 --> 00:01:59.050 line:80%
Be careful.

00:01:59.820 --> 00:02:00.660 line:80%
Goodbye.

00:02:06.490 --> 00:02:07.620 line:80%
Look carefully.

00:02:08.090 --> 00:02:09.020 line:80%
Leave no one alive.

00:02:09.370 --> 00:02:10.210 line:80%
Yes.

00:02:21.340 --> 00:02:22.620 line:80%
I have

00:02:22.860 --> 00:02:24.780 line:80%
the Ziwei Method.

00:02:30.410 --> 00:02:32.060 line:80%
I am a member of the Six Sects.

00:02:32.650 --> 00:02:35.090 line:80%
How could I collude
with the demonic sect?

00:02:35.340 --> 00:02:36.970 line:80%
Elder Tianji has long been dead.

00:02:37.210 --> 00:02:38.090 line:80%
Zhao,

00:02:38.090 --> 00:02:39.620 line:80%
don't listen to his slander.

00:02:39.620 --> 00:02:41.060 line:80%
At a time like this,

00:02:41.060 --> 00:02:43.140 line:80%
what is there left to hide?

00:02:43.140 --> 00:02:45.180 line:80%
When you and Elder Tianji came to me,

00:02:45.180 --> 00:02:46.900 line:80%
you said that with the Ziwei Method,

00:02:46.900 --> 00:02:49.650 line:80%
we wouldn't have to be
anyone's lackey anymore

00:02:49.650 --> 00:02:51.530 line:80%
or do dirty, exhausting work.

00:02:51.530 --> 00:02:53.690 line:80%
You even said
that Zhou Zhizhen wasn't better

00:02:53.690 --> 00:02:56.340 line:80%
than you in fighting or capability,

00:02:56.460 --> 00:02:58.780 line:80%
so why couldn't you become the lord?

00:02:59.020 --> 00:02:59.860 line:80%
You said

00:02:59.860 --> 00:03:01.090 line:80%
you'd unify

00:03:01.090 --> 00:03:02.460 line:80%
the Six Sects soon.

00:03:02.460 --> 00:03:03.300 line:80%
Shut up.

00:03:03.810 --> 00:03:04.650 line:80%
Mr. Zhou,

00:03:05.340 --> 00:03:06.690 line:80%
you're so foolish.

00:03:07.090 --> 00:03:09.650 line:80%
Why would Elder Tianji pass
his martial arts to you?

00:03:09.650 --> 00:03:12.043 line:80%
If not to rope you in as an inside man
among the Six Sects,

00:03:12.140 --> 00:03:13.210 line:80%
that old jerk

00:03:14.140 --> 00:03:15.300 line:80%
would never have survived

00:03:15.460 --> 00:03:17.490 line:80%
in the Li Sect.

00:03:17.780 --> 00:03:19.810 line:80%
How could he cultivate the Ziwei Method?

00:03:20.410 --> 00:03:21.530 line:80%
Once I leave,

00:03:21.930 --> 00:03:23.740 line:80%
I will surely report to the Chief.

00:03:32.810 --> 00:03:34.090 line:80%
Cowardly scoundrel.

00:03:34.580 --> 00:03:35.860 line:80%
Sowing discord.

00:03:36.090 --> 00:03:36.930 line:80%
Master,

00:03:38.020 --> 00:03:39.860 line:80%
didn't we agree to practice in secret?

00:03:40.090 --> 00:03:41.530 line:80%
If you report to the Chief,

00:03:42.460 --> 00:03:44.140 line:80%
we won't be able to practice anymore.

00:03:46.020 --> 00:03:48.340 line:80%
Uncle Jiu knew you harbored
ulterior motives.

00:03:48.340 --> 00:03:49.479 line:80%
He had me keep an eye on you.

00:03:49.490 --> 00:03:51.340 line:80%
You really thought I fancied you

00:03:51.460 --> 00:03:53.460 line:80%
and was willing to be your deputy?

00:03:53.860 --> 00:03:54.700 line:80%
You...

00:04:01.650 --> 00:04:02.490 line:80%
Zhao,

00:04:03.180 --> 00:04:04.620 line:80%
hand over the saliva.

00:04:04.900 --> 00:04:07.580 line:80%
Our sects have been friends
for generations.

00:04:07.580 --> 00:04:09.210 line:80%
You are also about to marry Yuqi.

00:04:09.490 --> 00:04:10.860 line:80%
We will be family.

00:04:11.060 --> 00:04:11.900 line:80%
Now,

00:04:12.460 --> 00:04:13.650 line:80%
I've lost my son.

00:04:13.780 --> 00:04:15.580 line:80%
You and Yuqi are my children.

00:04:15.580 --> 00:04:17.460 line:80%
We can cultivate
the Ziwei Method together

00:04:17.460 --> 00:04:19.340 line:80%
and bring glory to our sects.

00:04:19.500 --> 00:04:20.340 line:80%
That way,

00:04:20.900 --> 00:04:22.780 line:80%
we won't have to be submissive

00:04:22.780 --> 00:04:24.820 line:80%
or be suppressed by other sects.

00:04:24.820 --> 00:04:25.900 line:80%
That's right, young lady.

00:04:26.210 --> 00:04:27.940 line:80%
I also admire Ms. Cai.

00:04:28.460 --> 00:04:29.900 line:80%
Once the Method is perfected,

00:04:29.900 --> 00:04:31.650 line:80%
we can go out to uphold justice.

00:04:32.050 --> 00:04:34.170 line:80%
That would not disgrace Ms. Cai's name.

00:04:34.690 --> 00:04:35.530 line:80%
Right?

00:04:35.530 --> 00:04:36.370 line:80%
Zhao?

00:04:40.410 --> 00:04:41.500 line:80%
That makes sense.

00:04:43.090 --> 00:04:44.290 line:80%
It's not impossible.

00:04:46.730 --> 00:04:47.570 line:80%
Here you go.

00:04:59.820 --> 00:05:00.970 line:80%
You're still alive.

00:05:01.090 --> 00:05:02.780 line:80%
Your lover is dead.

00:05:02.780 --> 00:05:04.650 line:80%
Of course, I'm still alive.

00:05:06.780 --> 00:05:07.780 line:80%
Uncle Jiu.

00:05:12.340 --> 00:05:13.610 line:80%
You're a junior.

00:05:13.850 --> 00:05:15.190 line:80%
I won't make things hard for you.

00:05:15.610 --> 00:05:16.900 line:80%
Hand over the saliva,

00:05:17.210 --> 00:05:18.460 line:80%
and you may leave.

00:05:19.940 --> 00:05:21.340 line:80%
Saliva in exchange for my life.

00:05:21.780 --> 00:05:22.900 line:80%
That's not a bad deal.

00:05:23.170 --> 00:05:24.610 line:80%
But this saliva

00:05:25.380 --> 00:05:26.460 line:80%
is only a little.

00:05:27.940 --> 00:05:30.140 line:80%
Is it enough for the three of you?

00:05:33.170 --> 00:05:35.730 line:80%
No matter which one of you I give it to,

00:05:35.970 --> 00:05:37.050 line:80%
the other two

00:05:37.970 --> 00:05:40.170 line:80%
will harbor hatred toward me

00:05:40.820 --> 00:05:42.500 line:80%
and want me dead.

00:05:44.530 --> 00:05:46.050 line:80%
Give it to me.

00:05:46.050 --> 00:05:48.210 line:80%
They won't dare act rashly.

00:05:49.340 --> 00:05:50.210 line:80%
I don't believe it.

00:05:51.290 --> 00:05:53.340 line:80%
Unless you kill them all.

00:05:58.970 --> 00:05:59.810 line:80%
No.

00:06:00.290 --> 00:06:01.780 line:80%
What if you fake your deaths

00:06:02.410 --> 00:06:04.530 line:80%
and escape?

00:06:04.970 --> 00:06:06.380 line:80%
Wouldn't I suffer a huge loss?

00:06:07.210 --> 00:06:08.380 line:80%
What do you want?

00:06:15.580 --> 00:06:18.020 line:80%
I want you to cut off

00:06:23.820 --> 00:06:25.410 line:80%
Zhou Zhiqin's head.

00:06:25.530 --> 00:06:27.170 line:80%
When his head is separated
from his body,

00:06:27.380 --> 00:06:28.900 line:80%
I will hand over the saliva.

00:06:29.210 --> 00:06:30.050 line:80%
Cai Zhao,

00:06:30.340 --> 00:06:31.460 line:80%
have you lost your mind?

00:06:31.850 --> 00:06:34.090 line:80%
If not for you letting
that damned man escape,

00:06:34.090 --> 00:06:35.820 line:80%
so many people wouldn't have died.

00:06:36.040 --> 00:06:37.860 line:80%
Go to the underworld
and atone for your sins.

00:06:39.650 --> 00:06:40.490 line:80%
Elder Duan,

00:06:41.210 --> 00:06:42.970 line:80%
don't listen to her sowing discord.

00:06:44.210 --> 00:06:46.410 line:80%
As expected

00:06:46.410 --> 00:06:47.940 line:80%
of that vile Cai Pingshu,

00:06:48.460 --> 00:06:50.210 line:80%
raising such a vicious little wretch.

00:06:50.650 --> 00:06:51.490 line:80%
Fine.

00:06:52.340 --> 00:06:53.340 line:80%
Since you say that,

00:06:53.970 --> 00:06:55.020 line:80%
let's perish together.

00:06:55.100 --> 00:06:55.940 line:80%
- Wait.
- No.

00:06:55.940 --> 00:06:57.020 line:80%
Let's talk it out.

00:06:57.140 --> 00:06:58.290 line:80%
Talk it out, huh?

00:06:58.650 --> 00:07:00.170 line:80%
Then will you speak properly?

00:07:00.580 --> 00:07:01.780 line:80%
From now on,

00:07:01.780 --> 00:07:03.090 line:80%
I don't want to hear a single word

00:07:03.090 --> 00:07:04.900 line:80%
disrespecting my aunt.

00:07:05.210 --> 00:07:06.460 line:80%
Uncle Jiu was just anxious.

00:07:06.460 --> 00:07:08.140 line:80%
He didn't mean to slight your aunt.

00:07:08.140 --> 00:07:09.340 line:80%
We won't say it anymore.

00:07:09.340 --> 00:07:10.180 line:80%
We won't.

00:07:13.500 --> 00:07:16.290 line:80%
Stop putting on airs before me.

00:07:16.730 --> 00:07:18.170 line:80%
If I'm unhappy,

00:07:18.290 --> 00:07:20.610 line:80%
I can let go of the saliva,

00:07:20.820 --> 00:07:21.700 line:80%
but you

00:07:22.780 --> 00:07:24.530 line:80%
must die.

00:07:24.530 --> 00:07:25.460 line:80%
Then die.

00:07:25.460 --> 00:07:26.300 line:80%
No, no.

00:07:30.580 --> 00:07:32.500 line:80%
Are you going to do it or not?

00:07:33.970 --> 00:07:35.290 line:80%
I'll count to three.

00:07:35.580 --> 00:07:36.420 line:80%
One.

00:07:37.650 --> 00:07:38.490 line:80%
Two.

00:07:39.090 --> 00:07:39.940 line:80%
Three!

00:07:39.940 --> 00:07:40.780 line:80%
Fine.

00:07:43.730 --> 00:07:44.850 line:80%
I agree.

00:07:47.090 --> 00:07:47.930 line:80%
Uncle Jiu.

00:07:48.210 --> 00:07:49.170 line:80%
Qinong,

00:07:50.210 --> 00:07:51.730 line:80%
I'm old.

00:07:52.140 --> 00:07:53.530 line:80%
I can't wait any longer.

00:07:54.460 --> 00:07:56.210 line:80%
Don't blame me.

00:08:35.100 --> 00:08:36.020 line:80%
Young lady,

00:08:36.290 --> 00:08:37.570 line:80%
there's no way out.

00:08:38.100 --> 00:08:39.410 line:80%
Hand over the saliva,

00:08:39.900 --> 00:08:41.170 line:80%
and I'll let you go.

00:08:44.500 --> 00:08:45.340 line:80%
Here you go.

00:08:50.620 --> 00:08:52.740 line:80%
You wretch. I'll kill you.

00:09:05.650 --> 00:09:06.860 line:80%
Why are you still here?

00:09:09.590 --> 00:09:10.450 line:80%
Jerk!

00:09:10.450 --> 00:09:11.500 line:80%
You're not dead?

00:09:12.100 --> 00:09:13.080 line:80%
You were waiting for me.

00:09:13.410 --> 00:09:14.250 line:80%
How would I dare die?

00:09:14.500 --> 00:09:15.340 line:80%
Impossible.

00:09:15.500 --> 00:09:17.860 line:80%
I saw you dragged away by the python.

00:09:18.140 --> 00:09:19.930 line:80%
That's true.

00:09:20.530 --> 00:09:22.650 line:80%
But the python hates heat.

00:09:23.050 --> 00:09:24.530 line:80%
When my mindful way circulates,

00:09:24.530 --> 00:09:25.650 line:80%
my whole body heats up.

00:09:25.930 --> 00:09:27.330 line:80%
So, the python let me go.

00:09:27.810 --> 00:09:29.220 line:80%
I was quite lucky.

00:09:29.930 --> 00:09:31.570 line:80%
I even met a friend.

00:09:42.140 --> 00:09:43.100 line:80%
Qian Xueshen?

00:09:48.290 --> 00:09:49.530 line:80%
Weren't you already...

00:09:49.780 --> 00:09:51.860 line:80%
He bribed Mr. Zhang
and swapped identities with him.

00:09:53.170 --> 00:09:54.810 line:80%
The one who died there was Mr. Zhang.

00:09:55.450 --> 00:09:56.650 line:80%
Normally, once a person dies,

00:09:56.860 --> 00:09:58.900 line:80%
the Body Shift will end.

00:09:59.410 --> 00:10:00.980 line:80%
But the corpse was destroyed at once.

00:10:01.530 --> 00:10:02.810 line:80%
So, it was flawless,

00:10:03.140 --> 00:10:05.650 line:80%
and his scheme succeeded.

00:10:09.100 --> 00:10:11.170 line:80%
You also placed the statue

00:10:11.570 --> 00:10:12.980 line:80%
of my ancestor Gu Qingkong?

00:10:15.410 --> 00:10:16.740 line:80%
It's the Jade Statue.

00:10:20.330 --> 00:10:21.450 line:80%
Were you trying

00:10:21.980 --> 00:10:23.380 line:80%
to lure us into the ice cave

00:10:23.530 --> 00:10:24.810 line:80%
to be attacked by the python?

00:10:28.330 --> 00:10:29.500 line:80%
Why did you do this?

00:10:31.900 --> 00:10:33.380 line:80%
Because this hunting lodge

00:10:34.500 --> 00:10:35.650 line:80%
is my home.

00:10:39.380 --> 00:10:40.220 line:80%
So,

00:10:40.740 --> 00:10:42.530 line:80%
you are the son of that family.

00:10:43.140 --> 00:10:44.980 line:80%
What was that hunter's surname again?

00:10:45.220 --> 00:10:47.930 line:80%
I can't quite remember.

00:10:48.290 --> 00:10:49.130 line:80%
Tao.

00:10:49.930 --> 00:10:51.410 line:80%
If I remember correctly,

00:10:51.980 --> 00:10:54.530 line:80%
that young wife was quite pretty.

00:10:54.530 --> 00:10:56.020 line:80%
That was my aunt.

00:10:58.620 --> 00:11:00.570 line:80%
She was even pregnant.

00:11:01.500 --> 00:11:02.810 line:80%
Fifteen years ago,

00:11:02.980 --> 00:11:05.140 line:80%
you should've long been buried
by the snow.

00:11:05.860 --> 00:11:07.570 line:80%
It was my father and uncle

00:11:07.570 --> 00:11:09.330 line:80%
who dug you out one by one

00:11:10.050 --> 00:11:11.690 line:80%
and brought you home to recover.

00:11:12.810 --> 00:11:13.650 line:80%
Hey, everyone.

00:11:13.650 --> 00:11:14.500 line:80%
Come and help.

00:11:15.500 --> 00:11:16.820 line:80%
- Here, Shu.
- Father.

00:11:17.620 --> 00:11:18.460 line:80%
Come on.

00:11:20.410 --> 00:11:22.140 line:80%
Some wandering martial folks

00:11:22.140 --> 00:11:23.273 line:80%
were searching for treasure,

00:11:23.690 --> 00:11:26.170 line:80%
using powder and causing an avalanche.

00:11:27.100 --> 00:11:29.330 line:80%
Luckily, we heard the noise

00:11:29.330 --> 00:11:30.220 line:80%
and dug them out.

00:11:30.530 --> 00:11:31.370 line:80%
Their lives

00:11:31.570 --> 00:11:32.620 line:80%
were barely saved.

00:11:33.290 --> 00:11:34.620 line:80%
But the first thing

00:11:35.100 --> 00:11:36.980 line:80%
you did after waking up

00:11:37.530 --> 00:11:40.570 line:80%
was to silence them.

00:11:48.810 --> 00:11:50.100 line:80%
You beasts.

00:11:50.100 --> 00:11:51.530 line:80%
I'll kill you!

00:12:16.780 --> 00:12:18.290 line:80%
My child is about to be born.

00:12:19.050 --> 00:12:20.500 line:80%
Please let me go.

00:12:26.980 --> 00:12:29.020 line:80%
In this barren, freezing land,

00:12:29.690 --> 00:12:31.290 line:80%
you're so delicate and pretty.

00:12:31.500 --> 00:12:33.410 line:80%
After all, they did save us.

00:12:33.780 --> 00:12:34.650 line:80%
Why not

00:12:35.530 --> 00:12:37.020 line:80%
let them die painlessly?

00:12:40.100 --> 00:12:41.380 line:80%
What a surprise

00:12:41.380 --> 00:12:43.290 line:80%
that you'd be so compassionate.

00:12:46.290 --> 00:12:48.380 line:80%
How pretty and delicate.

00:12:49.020 --> 00:12:50.690 line:80%
Don't worry. It won't hurt.

00:12:55.220 --> 00:12:56.060 line:80%
What a sin.

00:12:56.780 --> 00:12:58.290 line:80%
Stop pretending.

00:12:58.650 --> 00:13:00.020 line:80%
Wasn't this your suggestion?

00:13:00.740 --> 00:13:03.380 line:80%
"Though they weren't part of Jianghu,"

00:13:03.380 --> 00:13:05.570 line:80%
"they often helped travelers."

00:13:05.570 --> 00:13:07.290 line:80%
"If they said something"

00:13:07.290 --> 00:13:09.530 line:80%
"and let people know
a righteous sect member"

00:13:10.020 --> 00:13:12.860 line:80%
"like you were mingling with us,"

00:13:13.980 --> 00:13:16.220 line:80%
"Qingque Sect wouldn't spare you."

00:13:16.530 --> 00:13:17.500 line:80%
Now, you're pretending?

00:13:17.690 --> 00:13:18.570 line:80%
Who is it for?

00:13:20.620 --> 00:13:23.620 line:80%
If Nie Hengcheng were to learn

00:13:24.140 --> 00:13:26.900 line:80%
that you colluded with Elder Duan
to secretly cultivate his skill,

00:13:28.140 --> 00:13:29.170 line:80%
do you think

00:13:30.100 --> 00:13:31.620 line:80%
he would spare you?

00:13:31.630 --> 00:13:32.470 line:80%
What did you say?

00:13:32.470 --> 00:13:33.350 line:80%
Enough.

00:13:33.570 --> 00:13:35.170 line:80%
We're on the same side.

00:13:35.170 --> 00:13:36.100 line:80%
Why argue about this?

00:13:36.860 --> 00:13:38.170 line:80%
Let's hurry and find

00:13:38.170 --> 00:13:39.570 line:80%
the saliva of the Snow-Scale Beast.

00:13:39.930 --> 00:13:40.770 line:80%
Then

00:13:41.170 --> 00:13:43.020 line:80%
what about these corpses?

00:13:46.050 --> 00:13:47.290 line:80%
Burn them all.

00:13:47.980 --> 00:13:49.330 line:80%
Save them from reincarnation.

00:14:09.500 --> 00:14:11.050 line:80%
Failing to eradicate the roots

00:14:11.050 --> 00:14:12.740 line:80%
surely brings endless trouble.

00:14:12.980 --> 00:14:13.820 line:80%
Back then,

00:14:14.140 --> 00:14:16.570 line:80%
we actually missed you.

00:14:16.860 --> 00:14:19.330 line:80%
You were only 7 or 8 years.

00:14:19.570 --> 00:14:20.650 line:80%
Alone in the snowfields,

00:14:20.650 --> 00:14:22.050 line:80%
how did you survive until now?

00:14:22.290 --> 00:14:24.020 line:80%
I met my master, Master Qianmian.

00:14:24.290 --> 00:14:25.570 line:80%
He rescued me

00:14:26.020 --> 00:14:27.380 line:80%
and taught me all my skills.

00:14:28.930 --> 00:14:30.380 line:80%
After my master died,

00:14:31.900 --> 00:14:33.690 line:80%
I returned here.

00:15:46.140 --> 00:15:47.020 line:80%
Eat, Snow.

00:15:47.290 --> 00:15:49.100 line:80%
I'll go steal some cured meat tonight.

00:15:49.100 --> 00:15:50.486 line:80%
I'll come feed you again tomorrow.

00:16:15.690 --> 00:16:16.570 line:80%
Snow,

00:16:16.810 --> 00:16:18.220 line:80%
you've grown so big already.

00:16:28.339 --> 00:16:30.330 line:80%
I spread news everywhere
that the Snow-Scale Beast

00:16:30.330 --> 00:16:31.810 line:80%
had reappeared in the snow mountains,

00:16:32.380 --> 00:16:33.860 line:80%
luring the greedy ones here,

00:16:34.930 --> 00:16:36.930 line:80%
and then trapped them in the ice cave.

00:16:42.060 --> 00:16:45.180 line:80%
(Zhou Yulin, Peiqiong Manor)

00:16:52.050 --> 00:16:56.410 line:80%
You killed so many innocent people
for the saliva

00:16:56.410 --> 00:16:58.410 line:80%
and even caused the death of your son.

00:16:58.410 --> 00:17:00.050 line:80%
Even if you master
peerless martial arts,

00:17:00.170 --> 00:17:01.170 line:80%
what use is it?

00:17:02.810 --> 00:17:04.980 line:80%
I've always tried to lure you all here.

00:17:05.500 --> 00:17:07.500 line:80%
Unfortunately,
my identity was exposed midway

00:17:07.511 --> 00:17:09.039 line:80%
and I was captured by the demonic sect.

00:17:09.050 --> 00:17:10.780 line:80%
But heaven has eyes.

00:17:12.050 --> 00:17:13.180 line:80%
Miss Cai

00:17:13.500 --> 00:17:15.420 line:80%
brought me back here,

00:17:15.660 --> 00:17:19.460 line:80%
and I finally met the enemies.

00:17:20.020 --> 00:17:22.290 line:80%
I deliberately put the saliva
in your son's hands

00:17:22.700 --> 00:17:24.780 line:80%
to make you kill each other.

00:17:29.500 --> 00:17:30.810 line:80%
The saliva is yours?

00:17:30.810 --> 00:17:31.660 line:80%
That's right.

00:17:32.500 --> 00:17:34.980 line:80%
The Snow-Scale Beast did appear here.

00:17:35.460 --> 00:17:36.740 line:80%
When I was little,

00:17:36.963 --> 00:17:38.610 line:80%
my father and uncle collected
quite a bit

00:17:38.610 --> 00:17:40.330 line:80%
of the saliva that dripped
onto the ground.

00:17:40.810 --> 00:17:42.850 line:80%
Do you remember the bed you slept on?

00:17:43.050 --> 00:17:44.700 line:80%
Fifteen years ago,

00:17:44.700 --> 00:17:46.500 line:80%
the saliva of the Snow-Scale Beast

00:17:47.220 --> 00:17:49.740 line:80%
was in the ice chest under the bed.

00:17:50.220 --> 00:17:52.420 line:80%
You didn't have to wait for 15 years.

00:17:54.420 --> 00:17:56.130 line:80%
Take out the remaining slime.

00:17:56.530 --> 00:17:58.660 line:80%
The last beast is already dead.

00:17:59.460 --> 00:18:01.180 line:80%
What Miss Cai poured out just now

00:18:01.850 --> 00:18:04.660 line:80%
was indeed the last saliva in the world.

00:18:05.740 --> 00:18:06.740 line:80%
You're lying.

00:18:07.740 --> 00:18:09.290 line:80%
There must still be saliva.

00:18:09.570 --> 00:18:11.420 line:80%
Take out the remaining slime.

00:18:11.420 --> 00:18:12.260 line:80%
Don't.

00:18:12.370 --> 00:18:13.390 line:80%
My wounds haven't healed.

00:18:13.460 --> 00:18:14.300 line:80%
I can't win.

00:18:14.686 --> 00:18:16.530 line:80%
- We'll find a chance to leave.
- Take it out.

00:18:16.530 --> 00:18:17.980 line:80%
- Leave him to later.
- Take it out.

00:18:17.980 --> 00:18:19.020 line:80%
Take it out.

00:18:23.610 --> 00:18:24.460 line:80%
What is this?

00:18:24.780 --> 00:18:26.810 line:80%
This is gland fluid I extracted
from the bodies

00:18:26.810 --> 00:18:28.220 line:80%
of a thousand female snakes.

00:18:28.530 --> 00:18:30.050 line:80%
Once male snakes smell it, they go mad.

00:18:30.370 --> 00:18:31.500 line:80%
No matter where you flee,

00:18:31.500 --> 00:18:32.780 line:80%
they will devour you

00:18:34.940 --> 00:18:36.500 line:80%
until death.

00:18:51.420 --> 00:18:52.260 line:80%
Qinong.

00:18:52.500 --> 00:18:54.420 line:80%
Come and help me.

00:18:55.130 --> 00:18:55.980 line:80%
Qinong.

00:19:01.330 --> 00:19:02.170 line:80%
Qian Xueshen!

00:19:30.570 --> 00:19:31.940 line:80%
I have the Ziwei Method.

00:19:32.050 --> 00:19:33.180 line:80%
I have the Ziwei Method.

00:19:33.180 --> 00:19:34.020 line:80%
Tell me.

00:19:34.130 --> 00:19:35.780 line:80%
Has Nie Zhe's Wudu Palm been perfected?

00:19:36.570 --> 00:19:37.810 line:80%
It's you.

00:19:38.050 --> 00:19:39.420 line:80%
Go, Qian Xueshen.

00:19:39.420 --> 00:19:40.890 line:80%
Why save me?

00:19:41.740 --> 00:19:42.850 line:80%
You're not a bad person.

00:19:43.090 --> 00:19:44.050 line:80%
You shouldn't die.

00:19:44.050 --> 00:19:45.220 line:80%
I'm not a bad person?

00:19:45.460 --> 00:19:46.660 line:80%
Are you blind?

00:19:47.530 --> 00:19:48.940 line:80%
I wanted to die long ago.

00:19:49.290 --> 00:19:50.130 line:80%
Qian Xueshen,

00:19:50.183 --> 00:19:51.660 line:80%
your whole family is dead except you.

00:19:51.736 --> 00:19:53.563 line:80%
When you reunite
with them in the underworld,

00:19:53.574 --> 00:19:55.094 line:80%
your parents will surely be delighted.

00:20:03.460 --> 00:20:04.420 line:80%
Mu Qingyan!

00:20:04.420 --> 00:20:06.050 line:80%
The avalanche! Run!

00:20:50.290 --> 00:20:51.130 line:80%
Zhao.

00:20:57.220 --> 00:20:58.060 line:80%
Zhao.

00:21:30.610 --> 00:21:31.890 line:80%
Where is this?

00:21:34.780 --> 00:21:35.780 line:80%
Where is Qian Xueshen?

00:21:39.290 --> 00:21:41.530 line:80%
Once you woke up, you asked about him.

00:21:43.313 --> 00:21:44.980 line:80%
Why don't you think
about how to repay me?

00:21:45.740 --> 00:21:46.850 line:80%
I have no money.

00:21:47.660 --> 00:21:48.500 line:80%
Just my life.

00:21:55.740 --> 00:21:57.740 line:80%
Even if you ask me
to give myself to you,

00:21:57.786 --> 00:21:59.130 line:80%
at most it's one night of passion.

00:21:59.346 --> 00:22:00.890 line:80%
I won't take responsibility afterward.

00:22:06.860 --> 00:22:08.540 line:80%
♪In days gone by♪

00:22:08.570 --> 00:22:09.410 line:80%
It's fine.

00:22:10.750 --> 00:22:13.500 line:80%
♪I first saw you in the dimness♪

00:22:14.470 --> 00:22:15.660 line:80%
♪Amid the vast crowd♪

00:22:15.670 --> 00:22:17.140 line:80%
♪A fleeting glance♪

00:22:17.310 --> 00:22:18.220 line:80%
♪And then♪

00:22:19.660 --> 00:22:21.180 line:80%
One night of passion

00:22:21.940 --> 00:22:23.420 line:80%
is better than tasting

00:22:23.660 --> 00:22:24.850 line:80%
no sweetness at all.

00:22:25.840 --> 00:22:27.180 line:80%
♪Alas, we parted♪

00:22:27.190 --> 00:22:29.380 line:80%
♪Longing for your return♪

00:22:29.510 --> 00:22:30.460 line:80%
♪Moon waxes and wanes♪

00:22:30.470 --> 00:22:31.940 line:80%
♪Letters can't convey my thoughts♪

00:22:31.950 --> 00:22:32.980 line:80%
♪Scattered petals♪

00:22:32.990 --> 00:22:35.220 line:80%
♪Cover the ground♪

00:22:36.280 --> 00:22:38.540 line:80%
♪Such should be our meeting♪

00:22:38.740 --> 00:22:43.410 line:80%
♪Golden wind brushes the jade dew♪

00:22:43.420 --> 00:22:46.140 line:80%
♪Half shy, half joyful♪

00:22:46.350 --> 00:22:50.230 line:80%
♪Wanting to leave yet lingering♪

00:22:51.020 --> 00:22:53.590 line:80%
♪Such should be our meeting♪

00:22:53.770 --> 00:22:58.120 line:80%
♪Across the Magpie Bridge♪

00:22:58.450 --> 00:23:01.000 line:80%
♪Alas, peach blossoms have fallen♪

00:23:01.240 --> 00:23:07.120 line:80%
♪Tears are like pearls♪

00:23:23.416 --> 00:23:25.370 line:80%
The tri-colored peach blossoms
of Luoying Valley.

00:23:25.490 --> 00:23:26.940 line:80%
So, this place has quite a connection

00:23:26.940 --> 00:23:28.940 line:80%
with your Luoying Valley.

00:23:30.050 --> 00:23:30.890 line:80%
You're awake.

00:23:33.090 --> 00:23:34.460 line:80%
The landlady?

00:23:39.290 --> 00:23:41.700 line:80%
It must have been you two who saved us.

00:23:41.850 --> 00:23:44.290 line:80%
You soaked in the Wanzai Hot Spring
for quite some time.

00:23:44.436 --> 00:23:45.460 line:80%
Your injuries have healed.

00:23:45.460 --> 00:23:47.370 line:80%
Only one of his poisons
remains hard to remove.

00:23:47.780 --> 00:23:48.980 line:80%
Thank you.

00:23:49.940 --> 00:23:50.780 line:80%
Sit.

00:23:58.660 --> 00:23:59.500 line:80%
Senior,

00:24:00.173 --> 00:24:01.060 line:80%
where is Qian Xueshen?

00:24:01.280 --> 00:24:02.130 line:80%
Is he all right?

00:24:02.130 --> 00:24:03.530 line:80%
He's much sturdier than you.

00:24:03.850 --> 00:24:05.090 line:80%
He woke up yesterday.

00:24:10.980 --> 00:24:12.530 line:80%
Why is that pretty boy

00:24:13.290 --> 00:24:14.530 line:80%
still alive?

00:24:15.610 --> 00:24:17.370 line:80%
This is the pattern of Luoying Valley.

00:24:18.740 --> 00:24:19.780 line:80%
Senior, are you

00:24:20.500 --> 00:24:22.890 line:80%
a descendant of my ancestor,
Ms. Gu Qingkong?

00:24:26.940 --> 00:24:28.980 line:80%
This is my master's grandmaster,

00:24:29.780 --> 00:24:31.500 line:80%
your ancestor, Gu Qingkong,

00:24:32.740 --> 00:24:33.580 line:80%
Ms. Gu.

00:24:35.290 --> 00:24:36.290 line:80%
200 years ago,

00:24:36.301 --> 00:24:38.799 line:80%
Founder Beichen summoned spirit beasts
from the immortal realm

00:24:38.810 --> 00:24:39.940 line:80%
to eradicate demons.

00:24:40.223 --> 00:24:43.120 line:80%
Later, martial practitioners discovered
that spirit beasts were helpful.

00:24:43.370 --> 00:24:44.420 line:80%
They forgot gratitude

00:24:44.420 --> 00:24:45.660 line:80%
and slaughtered them wantonly.

00:24:46.420 --> 00:24:48.050 line:80%
Ms. Gu, to protect the spirit beasts,

00:24:48.700 --> 00:24:50.570 line:80%
stood against all martial practitioners.

00:24:50.940 --> 00:24:52.610 line:80%
But no matter how gifted she was,

00:24:52.850 --> 00:24:54.850 line:80%
she could not withstand
endless human greed.

00:24:55.810 --> 00:24:56.650 line:80%
In the end,

00:24:56.980 --> 00:24:59.420 line:80%
she could only flee here
with the surviving spirit beasts

00:25:01.020 --> 00:25:02.420 line:80%
and vanish without a trace.

00:25:02.980 --> 00:25:04.740 line:80%
That's our first demoness.

00:25:04.890 --> 00:25:05.810 line:80%
Independent

00:25:06.050 --> 00:25:06.980 line:80%
and exceptional.

00:25:07.370 --> 00:25:09.810 line:80%
They say your demonesses defy the world

00:25:09.810 --> 00:25:10.980 line:80%
and are intolerable to all.

00:25:11.130 --> 00:25:12.570 line:80%
Why are you so proud about it?

00:25:12.940 --> 00:25:14.890 line:80%
They were smeared
because they were invincible.

00:25:15.460 --> 00:25:16.300 line:80%
No need to mind it.

00:25:17.660 --> 00:25:18.500 line:80%
Zhao is right.

00:25:19.570 --> 00:25:22.460 line:80%
Those people are simply shameless.

00:25:24.700 --> 00:25:25.610 line:80%
By the way, senior,

00:25:25.610 --> 00:25:26.850 line:80%
does the Snow-Scale Beast

00:25:27.810 --> 00:25:29.940 line:80%
still live today?

00:25:30.370 --> 00:25:31.810 line:80%
When your aunt came back then,

00:25:32.220 --> 00:25:35.890 line:80%
the last Snow-Scale Beast
was already at death's door.

00:25:36.090 --> 00:25:36.980 line:80%
My aunt came here?

00:25:38.500 --> 00:25:40.050 line:80%
She also came to look for the saliva.

00:25:41.130 --> 00:25:44.090 line:80%
A masked man traveled with her.

00:25:44.570 --> 00:25:47.530 line:80%
This painting was drawn by that man.

00:25:51.290 --> 00:25:53.740 line:80%
(Uncle Zhou and Master are upright.)

00:25:53.850 --> 00:25:55.130 line:80%
(They shouldn't have worn masks.)

00:25:56.780 --> 00:25:58.810 line:80%
Why did my aunt seek the saliva,

00:25:58.810 --> 00:26:00.050 line:80%
and who was that man?

00:26:00.530 --> 00:26:03.460 line:80%
Have you known Qian Xueshen
for a long time?

00:26:04.130 --> 00:26:07.420 line:80%
The Tao family often brought prey
to my master and me.

00:26:07.850 --> 00:26:09.570 line:80%
Shu and I grew up together.

00:26:09.793 --> 00:26:11.180 line:80%
The inn at the foot of the mountain

00:26:11.460 --> 00:26:13.500 line:80%
was set up to avenge the Tao family.

00:26:13.810 --> 00:26:15.660 line:80%
First, to gather information.

00:26:16.220 --> 00:26:17.060 line:80%
Second,

00:26:17.420 --> 00:26:20.290 line:80%
to stop innocent people
from dying senselessly.

00:26:20.740 --> 00:26:22.940 line:80%
Since you were so close
to the Tao family,

00:26:23.500 --> 00:26:24.340 line:80%
then

00:26:24.700 --> 00:26:26.420 line:80%
why didn't you intervene

00:26:26.940 --> 00:26:28.610 line:80%
the night they were killed?

00:26:32.810 --> 00:26:33.650 line:80%
At that time,

00:26:34.020 --> 00:26:36.780 line:80%
I was away seeking spirit medicine
for the dying Snow-Scale Beast.

00:26:37.330 --> 00:26:38.460 line:80%
I wasn't on the mountain.

00:26:39.020 --> 00:26:40.610 line:80%
The Tao family were all kind people

00:26:41.090 --> 00:26:42.700 line:80%
and saved many travelers.

00:26:43.130 --> 00:26:44.290 line:80%
Who could have expected

00:26:44.810 --> 00:26:45.890 line:80%
that this world

00:26:46.890 --> 00:26:48.020 line:80%
and the people of Jianghu

00:26:49.050 --> 00:26:50.290 line:80%
had never changed?

00:26:51.500 --> 00:26:52.570 line:80%
Where is Qian Xueshen?

00:26:58.370 --> 00:26:59.220 line:80%
Qian Xueshen.

00:27:00.940 --> 00:27:02.220 line:80%
My name is not Qian Xueshen.

00:27:04.980 --> 00:27:06.050 line:80%
My name is Tao Shu.

00:27:06.420 --> 00:27:07.260 line:80%
Miss Cai.

00:27:07.850 --> 00:27:08.690 line:80%
Mr. Mu.

00:27:08.980 --> 00:27:10.493 line:80%
Thank you for helping me avenge them.

00:27:10.700 --> 00:27:11.890 line:80%
No need to thank us.

00:27:12.220 --> 00:27:13.060 line:80%
In the end,

00:27:13.220 --> 00:27:14.980 line:80%
all sects owe you a debt.

00:27:16.700 --> 00:27:17.540 line:80%
Qian...

00:27:18.090 --> 00:27:18.930 line:80%
Shu,

00:27:20.050 --> 00:27:21.660 line:80%
is there still even a little

00:27:21.940 --> 00:27:23.420 line:80%
of the Snow-Scale Beast's saliva left?

00:27:25.130 --> 00:27:26.460 line:80%
Has the Snow-Scale Beast

00:27:26.780 --> 00:27:28.500 line:80%
left behind

00:27:28.980 --> 00:27:29.820 line:80%
anything else?

00:27:31.660 --> 00:27:32.810 line:80%
Xuegu once said

00:27:33.740 --> 00:27:35.660 line:80%
the Snow-Scale Beast
seemed to have left an egg.

00:27:42.220 --> 00:27:44.530 line:80%
A Snow-Scale Beast lays eggs?

00:27:46.610 --> 00:27:48.890 line:80%
Ancient dragons reproduce by eggs.

00:27:49.220 --> 00:27:50.890 line:80%
But this egg has been laid
for many years

00:27:51.090 --> 00:27:52.220 line:80%
and still refuses to hatch.

00:27:52.610 --> 00:27:53.980 line:80%
Didn't you raise Peng birds before?

00:27:54.085 --> 00:27:55.592 line:80%
You should know how to incubate eggs.

00:27:55.890 --> 00:27:58.090 line:80%
Call over your two Golden Pengs
to hatch it.

00:27:58.330 --> 00:27:59.460 line:80%
My Golden Pengs are male.

00:28:00.050 --> 00:28:01.020 line:80%
Both of them?

00:28:02.050 --> 00:28:03.130 line:80%
That's too cruel of you.

00:28:03.130 --> 00:28:04.050 line:80%
I...

00:28:04.050 --> 00:28:06.220 line:80%
Peng birds and dragon beasts
are natural enemies.

00:28:06.264 --> 00:28:07.769 line:80%
Dragon beasts are spiritual creatures.

00:28:07.780 --> 00:28:08.740 line:80%
If they sense danger,

00:28:08.940 --> 00:28:10.020 line:80%
they will never hatch.

00:28:10.530 --> 00:28:12.050 line:80%
Using Peng birds won't work.

00:28:13.020 --> 00:28:14.180 line:80%
My father once said

00:28:15.530 --> 00:28:18.090 line:80%
that ancient spirit beasts resonate
with their masters.

00:28:18.330 --> 00:28:20.780 line:80%
They rely on recognizing blood aura

00:28:21.460 --> 00:28:22.530 line:80%
to form a bond.

00:28:23.090 --> 00:28:24.460 line:80%
Since this Snow-Scale Beast

00:28:24.850 --> 00:28:26.700 line:80%
was saved by Luoying Valley's ancestor,

00:28:27.130 --> 00:28:28.556 line:80%
and they'd lived together for years,

00:28:28.940 --> 00:28:30.610 line:80%
it must recognize that blood aura.

00:28:32.050 --> 00:28:33.020 line:80%
Perhaps

00:28:35.220 --> 00:28:36.890 line:80%
the blood aura of Luoying Valley

00:28:38.130 --> 00:28:39.370 line:80%
can awaken it.

00:28:53.890 --> 00:28:54.940 line:80%
Did your father say

00:28:55.180 --> 00:28:57.180 line:80%
how much blood is needed
to raise a spirit beast?

00:28:57.370 --> 00:28:58.660 line:80%
I've been weak in blood aura.

00:28:58.660 --> 00:29:00.050 line:80%
I don't know if it'll work.

00:29:12.130 --> 00:29:12.970 line:80%
Look.

00:29:13.290 --> 00:29:14.130 line:80%
It didn't work.

00:29:15.180 --> 00:29:16.180 line:80%
That shouldn't be.

00:29:17.330 --> 00:29:18.170 line:80%
Again.

00:29:24.850 --> 00:29:25.740 line:80%
Mu Qingyan!

00:29:25.740 --> 00:29:26.580 line:80%
Look.

00:29:51.330 --> 00:29:53.050 line:80%
Dragon.

00:30:00.180 --> 00:30:01.460 line:80%
So good.

00:30:03.220 --> 00:30:04.060 line:80%
Dragon.

00:30:04.530 --> 00:30:06.220 line:80%
Spit out some saliva.

00:30:10.130 --> 00:30:11.180 line:80%
You've got nerve.

00:30:12.290 --> 00:30:13.290 line:80%
Come on.

00:30:13.301 --> 00:30:14.460 line:80%
If you don't spit out saliva,

00:30:14.460 --> 00:30:15.483 line:80%
I'll stew you into soup.

00:30:22.980 --> 00:30:23.820 line:80%
Get down here.

00:30:26.090 --> 00:30:26.996 line:80%
If you don't come down,

00:30:27.220 --> 00:30:28.130 line:80%
I'll braise you.

00:30:30.850 --> 00:30:31.690 line:80%
Don't run.

00:30:33.290 --> 00:30:34.180 line:80%
Don't run.

00:30:36.180 --> 00:30:37.173 line:80%
I'll chop you into mince

00:30:37.370 --> 00:30:38.210 line:80%
and make wonton.

00:30:54.500 --> 00:30:56.420 line:80%
Give me some.

00:30:56.420 --> 00:30:58.130 line:80%
Please.

00:31:00.940 --> 00:31:02.130 line:80%
Come on.

00:31:11.810 --> 00:31:12.780 line:80%
I'm telling you.

00:31:13.500 --> 00:31:14.940 line:80%
Behave,

00:31:15.330 --> 00:31:16.660 line:80%
or I'll kill you.

00:31:28.220 --> 00:31:30.370 line:80%
(Isn't this Grandfather's mechanism?)

00:31:33.130 --> 00:31:34.090 line:80%
It fell asleep.

00:31:35.180 --> 00:31:36.700 line:80%
So cute.

00:31:39.330 --> 00:31:41.660 line:80%
Once I get the saliva
and find my master,

00:31:41.780 --> 00:31:43.220 line:80%
I'll come back to keep it company.

00:31:46.780 --> 00:31:48.570 line:80%
You complain for three days

00:31:48.739 --> 00:31:50.312 line:80%
just because a wonton has no scallions.

00:31:50.530 --> 00:31:53.020 line:80%
Someone so attached to worldly pleasures

00:31:53.810 --> 00:31:56.330 line:80%
could hardly last three days

00:31:57.570 --> 00:31:58.780 line:80%
on this cold, silent snow peak.

00:31:59.250 --> 00:32:00.700 line:80%
And you want to live here long-term?

00:32:02.780 --> 00:32:04.130 line:80%
Why say it out loud?

00:32:11.020 --> 00:32:12.700 line:80%
I selfishly forced it

00:32:13.370 --> 00:32:15.090 line:80%
to hatch.

00:32:15.890 --> 00:32:19.570 line:80%
There's only one Snow-Scale Beast
in this world.

00:32:20.180 --> 00:32:21.530 line:80%
It must be very lonely.

00:32:22.290 --> 00:32:24.180 line:80%
The Snow-Scale Beast
lives a very long life.

00:32:24.500 --> 00:32:26.530 line:80%
At least 200 years.

00:32:26.810 --> 00:32:28.736 line:80%
In 200 years, the world
will change many times.

00:32:29.020 --> 00:32:30.530 line:80%
Maybe somewhere out there,

00:32:30.810 --> 00:32:32.570 line:80%
another of its kind will appear.

00:32:32.780 --> 00:32:33.620 line:80%
So,

00:32:34.530 --> 00:32:35.890 line:80%
we ordinary mortals

00:32:36.850 --> 00:32:38.290 line:80%
needn't rack our brains worrying

00:32:38.570 --> 00:32:41.460 line:80%
about this long-lived little creature.

00:32:44.700 --> 00:32:46.810 line:80%
You seem pretty concerned yourself.

00:32:46.940 --> 00:32:48.570 line:80%
How would I care

00:32:49.290 --> 00:32:51.500 line:80%
about a little spirit beast?

00:32:51.850 --> 00:32:52.690 line:80%
Really?

00:33:05.050 --> 00:33:06.180 line:80%
Hard work pays off.

00:33:06.500 --> 00:33:07.610 line:80%
We finally got it.

00:33:15.460 --> 00:33:16.610 line:80%
But can this thing

00:33:17.850 --> 00:33:19.850 line:80%
really counter the Body Shift?

00:33:26.780 --> 00:33:27.620 line:80%
Don't move.

00:33:34.890 --> 00:33:35.740 line:80%
Young Master,

00:33:36.220 --> 00:33:37.060 line:80%
forgive me.

00:33:57.370 --> 00:33:58.940 line:80%
Why turn me into a woman?

00:34:09.540 --> 00:34:11.060 line:80%
After taking the saliva,

00:34:11.060 --> 00:34:12.466 line:80%
it takes two hours to take effect.

00:34:14.410 --> 00:34:15.740 line:80%
What if I can't change back?

00:34:15.740 --> 00:34:16.660 line:80%
Rest assured.

00:34:16.660 --> 00:34:17.500 line:80%
You will.

00:34:18.060 --> 00:34:19.850 line:80%
I have something to do. I'll go first.

00:34:23.540 --> 00:34:25.580 line:80%
Anyway, the antidote takes two hours.

00:34:25.740 --> 00:34:26.882 line:80%
Since you have nothing to do,

00:34:26.893 --> 00:34:27.813 line:80%
do me a favor.

00:34:28.010 --> 00:34:29.580 line:80%
Whatever is in your mind,

00:34:29.970 --> 00:34:30.890 line:80%
it's impossible.

00:34:30.890 --> 00:34:32.370 line:80%
Mu.

00:34:32.930 --> 00:34:35.810 line:80%
I even borrowed these clothes for you.

00:34:51.850 --> 00:34:52.810 line:80%
Xuegu?

00:34:53.330 --> 00:34:54.170 line:80%
Senior,

00:34:54.930 --> 00:34:56.450 line:80%
Xuegu wants to ask you

00:34:56.740 --> 00:34:58.370 line:80%
why you hid your identity from her.

00:34:58.780 --> 00:35:00.220 line:80%
Qian Xueshen said you have no name

00:35:00.220 --> 00:35:01.100 line:80%
and belong to no sect.

00:35:01.450 --> 00:35:03.330 line:80%
Why do you know
the Ning clan's mechanisms?

00:35:03.810 --> 00:35:04.650 line:80%
Could it be...

00:35:04.660 --> 00:35:05.540 line:80%
Is your mother well?

00:35:06.010 --> 00:35:06.850 line:80%
Uncle?

00:35:07.700 --> 00:35:09.450 line:80%
My mother said
you disappeared 15 years ago.

00:35:09.660 --> 00:35:11.060 line:80%
Everyone thought you were dead.

00:35:11.410 --> 00:35:12.740 line:80%
I have been reborn.

00:35:12.890 --> 00:35:14.010 line:80%
The past

00:35:14.010 --> 00:35:14.970 line:80%
no longer counts.

00:35:16.660 --> 00:35:17.500 line:80%
Mr. Mu.

00:35:18.330 --> 00:35:20.850 line:80%
Is this the Qianmian Sect's Body Shift?

00:35:22.140 --> 00:35:22.980 line:80%
Uncle,

00:35:23.100 --> 00:35:24.930 line:80%
you even recognized him?

00:35:24.930 --> 00:35:27.049 line:80%
Xuegu and I have known each other
for over ten years.

00:35:27.060 --> 00:35:29.010 line:80%
I can tell at a glance.

00:35:29.290 --> 00:35:30.850 line:80%
Mr. Ning, sharp eyes indeed.

00:35:31.620 --> 00:35:32.460 line:80%
Uncle,

00:35:32.740 --> 00:35:35.290 line:80%
my mother and great-aunt
often think of you.

00:35:35.540 --> 00:35:36.810 line:80%
When do you plan to return?

00:35:40.810 --> 00:35:41.650 line:80%
I won't.

00:35:41.930 --> 00:35:43.140 line:80%
The world is dull.

00:35:43.290 --> 00:35:44.810 line:80%
My beloved matters more.

00:35:45.710 --> 00:35:46.780 line:80%
Xuegu is about to wake up.

00:35:47.010 --> 00:35:49.620 line:80%
I need to brew tea
and cook congee for her.

00:35:59.700 --> 00:36:01.100 line:80%
It really works.

00:36:02.010 --> 00:36:02.930 line:80%
We can go back.

00:36:02.930 --> 00:36:04.330 line:80%
We'll depart early tomorrow morning.

00:36:05.010 --> 00:36:06.140 line:80%
Uncle warned me

00:36:06.490 --> 00:36:08.410 line:80%
not to reveal the snow mountains
or his matters,

00:36:09.410 --> 00:36:12.330 line:80%
so the spirit beasts and they
can have their last pure land.

00:36:14.220 --> 00:36:15.410 line:80%
Once we part,

00:36:17.850 --> 00:36:20.490 line:80%
I don't think we'll meet again.

00:36:24.490 --> 00:36:25.330 line:80%
Zhao,

00:36:27.370 --> 00:36:28.810 line:80%
would you give up everything

00:36:30.180 --> 00:36:31.330 line:80%
for the one you love?

00:36:36.140 --> 00:36:37.100 line:80%
Of course not.

00:36:37.660 --> 00:36:38.500 line:80%
As you said,

00:36:38.620 --> 00:36:40.220 line:80%
I'm attached to the bustling world.

00:36:40.660 --> 00:36:41.500 line:80%
Besides,

00:36:41.740 --> 00:36:43.033 line:80%
I haven't become the Manager yet.

00:36:43.540 --> 00:36:45.280 line:80%
How could I give up everything
for someone?

00:36:46.580 --> 00:36:47.780 line:80%
What if it were for me?

00:36:48.490 --> 00:36:49.330 line:80%
For you?

00:36:53.100 --> 00:36:54.140 line:80%
I'd be even less willing.

00:36:54.700 --> 00:36:55.620 line:80%
Think about it.

00:36:55.620 --> 00:36:58.060 line:80%
The Lord of Qianmian Sect
made a wrong choice

00:36:58.410 --> 00:37:00.580 line:80%
and ruined the entire sect.

00:37:00.890 --> 00:37:02.660 line:80%
The past warns the future.

00:37:03.450 --> 00:37:04.930 line:80%
I wouldn't do something that foolish.

00:37:07.410 --> 00:37:08.410 line:80%
You're right.

00:37:10.100 --> 00:37:10.940 line:80%
What about you?

00:37:12.930 --> 00:37:14.700 line:80%
Would you give up everything
for someone?

00:37:15.140 --> 00:37:15.980 line:80%
I would.

00:37:16.810 --> 00:37:17.650 line:80%
I don't believe it.

00:37:18.370 --> 00:37:19.700 line:80%
There's nothing I can't give up.

00:37:21.100 --> 00:37:22.780 line:80%
As the Young Master,

00:37:22.970 --> 00:37:24.970 line:80%
you'll surely have
piles of gold and silver,

00:37:24.970 --> 00:37:26.100 line:80%
wives and concubines aplenty,

00:37:26.100 --> 00:37:27.330 line:80%
fine clothes, and rich food.

00:37:27.490 --> 00:37:29.490 line:80%
You have everything to give up,

00:37:29.850 --> 00:37:31.290 line:80%
but you just can't.

00:37:31.850 --> 00:37:33.580 line:80%
Is that how you see the life

00:37:33.930 --> 00:37:34.850 line:80%
of the Young Master?

00:37:35.290 --> 00:37:36.130 line:80%
Then what is it like?

00:37:59.450 --> 00:38:00.410 line:80%
What a lousy bird,

00:38:00.410 --> 00:38:01.580 line:80%
wanting to eat a little beast.

00:38:03.930 --> 00:38:05.140 line:80%
They're natural enemies,

00:38:06.373 --> 00:38:07.490 line:80%
locked in deadly opposition

00:38:07.490 --> 00:38:09.700 line:80%
for generations.

00:38:09.700 --> 00:38:10.540 line:80%
Just like the Li Sect

00:38:10.540 --> 00:38:12.010 line:80%
and your Six Sects.

00:38:13.740 --> 00:38:15.580 line:80%
As long as you're happy.

00:38:18.890 --> 00:38:20.450 line:80%
You really aren't coming with us?

00:38:20.810 --> 00:38:23.060 line:80%
This frozen wilderness is deserted.

00:38:23.620 --> 00:38:24.850 line:80%
My uncle stayed for Xuegu.

00:38:25.010 --> 00:38:26.100 line:80%
Why are you staying?

00:38:26.290 --> 00:38:27.130 line:80%
For it.

00:38:31.700 --> 00:38:32.890 line:80%
The Snow-Scale Beast

00:38:33.290 --> 00:38:34.410 line:80%
or the Body Shift

00:38:35.010 --> 00:38:36.736 line:80%
never should have reappeared
in this world.

00:38:37.620 --> 00:38:39.180 line:80%
I couldn't let go of this skin.

00:38:39.369 --> 00:38:41.255 line:80%
Consider me leaving an heir
for the Tao family.

00:38:42.850 --> 00:38:44.930 line:80%
This is where my family
lived for generations.

00:38:45.410 --> 00:38:46.450 line:80%
Staying here,

00:38:47.220 --> 00:38:48.220 line:80%
I feel at ease.

00:38:48.780 --> 00:38:50.370 line:80%
I'll raise the little dragon beast.

00:38:52.010 --> 00:38:52.890 line:80%
Ms. Cai.

00:38:53.060 --> 00:38:53.900 line:80%
Mr. Mu.

00:38:54.370 --> 00:38:56.540 line:80%
Meeting you both was my fortune.

00:38:57.010 --> 00:38:58.660 line:80%
All banquets must end.

00:38:58.780 --> 00:38:59.620 line:80%
Let us

00:39:00.010 --> 00:39:01.140 line:80%
part here.

00:39:02.180 --> 00:39:03.020 line:80%
Take care.

00:39:03.330 --> 00:39:04.120 line:80%
Take care.

00:39:04.220 --> 00:39:05.060 line:80%
Take care.

00:39:12.370 --> 00:39:13.660 line:80%
(May we never meet again.)

00:39:15.290 --> 00:39:16.130 line:80%
(Zhao,)

00:39:16.930 --> 00:39:17.850 line:80%
(thank you.)

00:39:19.330 --> 00:39:20.580 line:80%
(Thank you for believing in me)

00:39:21.490 --> 00:39:24.100 line:80%
(and not giving up on me.)

00:39:53.410 --> 00:39:54.490 line:80%
Come and help.

00:40:01.410 --> 00:40:02.290 line:80%
People

00:40:02.290 --> 00:40:03.740 line:80%
are both good and bad.

00:40:04.620 --> 00:40:06.810 line:80%
Even if you save just one good person,

00:40:07.100 --> 00:40:08.140 line:80%
it's worth it.

00:40:08.530 --> 00:40:09.370 line:80%
Do you understand?

00:40:09.370 --> 00:40:10.410 line:80%
Mother.

00:40:12.140 --> 00:40:14.060 line:80%
Father. Mother.

00:40:15.370 --> 00:40:17.490 line:80%
If I encounter travelers in need again,

00:40:18.010 --> 00:40:20.540 line:80%
I will still save them,
just like you did.

00:40:22.220 --> 00:40:23.850 line:80%
You were never wrong.

00:40:24.580 --> 00:40:26.620 line:80%
Those who do evil are.

00:40:36.401 --> 00:40:47.061 line:80%
=Generation to Generation=

00:41:05.821 --> 00:41:10.231 line:80%
♪The breeze is gentle,
and spring is fair♪

00:41:10.796 --> 00:41:15.411 line:80%
♪I roam the rivers and hills
in the martial world♪

00:41:15.751 --> 00:41:20.316 line:80%
♪With a shining cup,
I drink with delight tonight♪

00:41:20.841 --> 00:41:25.141 line:80%
♪Free to wander in the world♪

00:41:28.086 --> 00:41:32.786 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:41:33.311 --> 00:41:37.601 line:80%
♪I rest beneath the stars' soft gleam♪

00:41:38.261 --> 00:41:42.291 line:80%
♪The night is calm, still as a stream♪

00:41:42.606 --> 00:41:47.731 line:80%
♪It washes away all judgment and scheme♪

00:41:48.306 --> 00:41:53.116 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:41:53.331 --> 00:41:57.501 line:80%
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

00:41:58.226 --> 00:42:02.161 line:80%
♪I freely roam in the world♪

00:42:02.661 --> 00:42:07.936 line:80%
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪

00:42:30.666 --> 00:42:35.796 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:42:36.161 --> 00:42:40.531 line:80%
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

00:42:40.796 --> 00:42:44.926 line:80%
♪I freely roam in the world♪

00:42:45.111 --> 00:42:50.686 line:80%
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪